nt of view, the sum-capacity gain due to\nthe relay can now be thought as coming from either signal relaying only, or\ninterference forwarding only.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Sep 2011 00:21:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Nov 2011 23:30:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 15 Aug 2012 04:34:32 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 12 Dec 2012 07:33:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-12-13"}
