by four-electron coincidence detection technique in\nexperiment. Our calculation shows that this two-dimensional spectrum is useful\nin understanding contributions of CVV and VVVV states to the Auger decay of\nmolecular DCH states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Sep 2011 04:54:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
